  "id": "seed-html-012",
  "targetLanguage": "HTML",
  "instruction": "Write an HTML5 page with a skip link targeting the main landmark. The skip link must be the first focusable element in the body.",
  "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n  <head>\n    <meta charset=\"utf-8\" />\n    <title>Skip link page</title>\n  </head>\n  <body>\n    <a href=\"#main-content\">Skip to main content</a>\n    <header>\n      <h1>Support center</h1>\n      <nav aria-label=\"Primary\">\n        <ul>\n          <li><a href=\"/help\">Help</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/status\">Status</a></li>\n        </ul>\n      </nav>\n    </header>\n    <main id=\"main-content\">\n      <h2>Ticket history</h2>\n      <p>No open tickets.</p>\n    </main>\n  </body>\n</html>",
